

## ELMOS product convergence and reference implementation

Use `$conv-product-convergence-orchestrator` to consolidate Batch 1–45 into the unified product kernel and reference implementation. Prefer the smallest `$conv-*` skill for focused work. Do not claim mature-product readiness until `$conv-product-convergence-readiness-gate` passes with real Control Plane, Private Runner, Reference Route, two independent customer organizations, one independent review, unit economics, customer handoff, and immutable evidence.
